text: Liam Cunningham (born 2 June 1961) is an Irish stage and screen actor. He is known for playing Davos Seaworth in the HBO epic-fantasy series Game of Thrones. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1961 births Category:Irish movie actors Category:Irish television actors Category:Irish stage actors Category:Actors from Dublin Category:Living people
